                        <p class="place-address">내용 : {{content}} | 최대인원 : {{maxCapacity}} | 가격 : {{defaultPrice}} </p>
                        <p></p>
                        <a href="/place/{{roomId}}/room" class="btn btn-place">상세보기</a>

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-end mb-2">
                            <a href="/room/{{roomId}}/update" class="btn btn-update">수정</a>
                            <form action="/place/{{roomId}}/delete" method="post">
                                <button class="btn btn-delete">삭제</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/roomList}}
        </div>


        <div class="left">
            <div class="main-content">
                <p>어울림 스터디카페</p>
                <span><img src="/img/room/주소.png" alt=""> 부산광역시 부산진구 신천대로 62번길</span>
                <p>룸 선택</p>
